### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/mock-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "lab-review-v18"
}

> {%
client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### 上传并解析化验单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lab-reports/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="reportDate"

2026-05-02
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="lab-report.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./lab-report.png
--WebAppBoundary--

> {%
client.global.set("report_id", response.body.data.reportId);
%}

### 查看化验单列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lab-reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查看该份化验单复盘
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lab-reports/{{report_id}}/review
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
